Class Procedure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.magknight.route.proc.Procedure
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    APPR, SID, STAR

    public class Procedure
extends java.lang.Object
    Procedure class implements general procedure specifications to be extended by a derived class implementing a specific procedure type.
